opcode - package opcode
 
Orc - Class in entities.monsters
This class of Monster is an orc, another common enemy in many RPGs.
Orc() - Constructor for class entities.monsters.Orc
The base constructor of the Orc sets the name to "orc", HPmax to 15, HP to 15, strength to 10, defense to 6, speed to 4, and XPval to 20.
